"{\"uid\": \"egyptindependent.com-egypts-fencing-team-achieves-commendable-sixth-place-finish-at-paris-2024-olympic-games\", \"text\": \"The Egyptian fencing team (men's foil)secured sixth place in the ongoing Paris 2024 Olympic Games on Wednesday evening.  The Egyptian fencing team lost to its Italian counterpart 38-45 in the match to determine the fifth place for men's team foil at the ongoing Paris Olympics.  Egyptian trio Ziad al-Sisi, Mohamed Amer, and Adham Moataz, participated in the match.  Previously, the Egyptian team had defeated Canada 45-41, but was narrowly bested by France 41-45, ending their competition.  The 33rd Olympic Games commenced on July 26th and will conclude on August 11th.\"}"